  "description": {
    "main": "The Sony HT-A3000 Sound Bar brings you 3.1 channels of cinematic sound that'll make movies and TV shows much more immersive. The all-in-one design packs in a trio of X-Balanced front speakers (including a dedicated centre channel for better clarity) and a built-in dual subwoofer. You'll be feeling the full force of the action as it flows all around you with Dolby Atmos and DTS:X, both boosted by Sony's Vertical Surround Engine and S-Force PRO Front Surround. And to help you make the most of your sound bar, Sound Field Optimisation cleverly maps the layout of your room and tunes the sound accordingly.",
    "goodToKnow": [
      "Acoustic Center Sync technology perfectly aligns the sound bar with your Sony BRAVIA TV's speakers",
      "Fall in love with your favourite albums all over again with 360 Reality Audio",
      "Stream music with Spotify Connect, Chromecast or Apple AirPlay 2"
    ]
